parameters.name: Accessibility
parameters.description:
The visibility of the workspace.

*   PRIVATE: The workspace is visible only to you and the administrator of the workspace.
*   PUBLIC: The workspace is visible to all users.

parameters.name: Creator
parameters.description: The ID of the user who created the experiment.

parameters.name: IncludeConfigData
parameters.description: Specifies whether to include experiment configuration data in the response.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The keyword of the name of the experiment.

parameters.name: Order
parameters.description:
The sorting order. Specify this parameter together with the SortBy parameter. Valid values:

*   DESC: in descending order. This is the default value.
*   ASC: in ascending order.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. Pages start from page 1. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page.

parameters.name: SortBy
parameters.description: The filter that is used to sort experiments.
